# Templates

This folder contains the HTML templates used by the Viral Times project.  
Templates are organized by app for clarity.

## Outbreaks Templates
- **new_outbreak.html** – Form for creating a new outbreak entry
- **outbreak_detail.html** – Detailed view of a single outbreak
- **outbreak_list.html** – List view showing all outbreaks
- **welcome.html** – Landing page for the site

## Reports Templates
- **new_report.html** – Form for creating a new report entry
- **report_detail.html** – Detailed view of a single report
- **report_list.html** – List view showing all reports
